    {
        "content": "<p><span class=\"user-mention silent\" data-user-id=\"228466\">Chris Bailey</span> <a href=\"#narrow/stream/270676-lean4/topic/Implicit.20evidences.20with.20simp.20proofs/near/462600813\">said</a>:</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>The syntax for this is <code>(ident : ty := tactic)</code>:</p>\n<p><div class=\"codehilite\" data-code-language=\"Lean4\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"kn\">def</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">addNonzero</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">a</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">b</span><span class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">Nat</span><span class=\"o\">)</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">h</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">b</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">≠</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"mi\">0</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"k\">by</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">simp</span><span class=\"o\">)</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">a</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">+</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">b</span>\n\n<span class=\"c1\">-- ok</span>\n<span class=\"bp\">#</span><span class=\"n\">eval</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">addNonzero</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"mi\">1</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"mi\">2</span>\n<span class=\"c1\">-- fails</span>\n<span class=\"bp\">#</span><span class=\"n\">eval</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">addNonzero</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"mi\">1</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"mi\">0</span>\n</code></pre></div><br>\n</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>Wow perfect, exactly what I was looking for. Thanks</p>",
